    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced beef</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until lightly browned</p><p>Peel and slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong>, peel and finely chop (or grate) <strong>half</strong> your <strong>garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>and grate your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong></p><p>Once the beef is browned, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> grated mushroom </strong>and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and cook for 3 min further, then add your <strong>beef stock mix </strong>with<strong> </strong>400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[520ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[680ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>,<strong> </strong>your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and<strong> Henderson's Relish</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1674228718262-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1674228718262-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1674228718262-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1674228718262-x1000.jpg",
